"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2\">Additional Rate</p><p class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900\">£125,140</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">Reduced from £150k</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6\">Extra Tax You&#x27;re Paying</h2><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div><label class=\"block text-gray-900 font-semibold mb-3\">Your Salary</label><div class=\"flex gap-2 flex-wrap\"><button class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200\">£<!-- -->30<!-- -->k</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200\">£<!-- -->45<!-- -->k</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition font-medium bg-blue-600 text-white\">£<!-- -->60<!-- -->k</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200\">£<!-- -->80<!-- -->k</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200\">£<!-- -->100<!-- -->k</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200\">£<!-- -->150<!-- -->k</button></div></div><div><label class=\"block text-gray-900 font-semibold mb-3\">Time Horizon</label><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><button class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition font-medium bg-blue-600 text-white\">Current (2026)</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200\">+5 Years</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200\">+10 Years</button></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200\"><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl p-6\"><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2\">Total Extra Tax Paid</p><p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-red-600\">£<!-- -->5,903</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-xs mt-2\">Since frozen thresholds began (2021)</p></div><div class=\"bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200 rounded-xl p-6\"><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2\">Annual Impact</p><p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-orange-600\">£<!-- -->1,181</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-xs mt-2\">Average per year</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-2xl p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Fiscal Drag</h3><p class=\"text-gray-700\">You move into higher tax brackets purely due to inflation, not real income growth. This silently increases your tax burden year after year.</p></div><div class=\"bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Lost Purchasing Power</h3><p class=\"text-gray-700\">You&#x27;re paying more tax on the same real income. Your take-home pay doesn&#x27;t keep up with inflation, so you can afford less over time.</p></div></div></div></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-74c939c87fa0092a.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[9766,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[8924,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[1959,[],\\\"ClientPageRoot\\\"]\\n5:I[480,[\\\"82\\\",\\\"static/chunks/82-ded4c674cc53fd1d.js\\\",\\\"620\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/frozen-tax-bands/page-fdee704859733510.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[4431,[],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\na:I[5278,[],\\\"AsyncMetadataOutlet\\\"]\\nc:I[4431,[],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\ne:I[4431,[],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\nf:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\n11:I[7150,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/a4e6d173275a0807.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"b\\\":\\\"PWIcP1CxgzGw7irVeUIUg\\\",\\\"p\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"c\\\